raw_data.title: Software Engineer
raw_data.description: The Software Engineer designs, develops, tests, and maintains software applications and systems to meet client and organizational needs. They analyze user requirements, translate them into technical specifications, and apply programming languages, frameworks, and tools to build secure, efficient, and scalable solutions. Responsibilities include collaborating with cross-functional teams, performing code reviews, debugging, preparing technical documentation, and ensuring compliance with standards and best practices. The role also involves staying current with emerging technologies, supporting Agile development cycles, mentoring junior developers, and delivering solutions on time and within budget.
